      <tr><td>Migraines and sinus pressure cause debilitating pain<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">Tension headaches wake you up or prevent sleep entirely</span></td><td>Gentle acupressure weight + lavender aromatherapy provides natural relief<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">Consistent pressure around eyes/sinuses + scent = measurable tension reduction</span></td></tr>
