<!-- §9 What is [Product]? -->
<h2>What Is a Weighted Eye Mask and Why It Works</h2>
<p>A weighted eye mask is a blackout mask filled with a gentle, even weight that sits across your eyes and sinuses. Unlike regular sleep masks that just block light, the weight provides acupressure — consistent gentle pressure that triggers the parasympathetic nervous system (your "rest and digest" mode). The Heart Weighted Eye Mask takes this further by incorporating lavender, which has documented calming properties. Research on weighted blankets shows the same principle works across the body; the Heart mask focuses that benefit on the most sensitive area — your eyes and face.</p>

